high_descs: Stand up turn around walk towards the cabinet.
Pick up the wine bottle from the cabinet.
Turn around walk towards the counter top.
Keep the wine bottle on the top of the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the wine bottle from the cabinet and keep it on the top of the counter top.

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the cabinet.
Pick up watch from the desk.
Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the counter top.
Pick up wine bottle from the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Shifting wine bottle from one place to another.

high_descs: Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the cabinet on your right.
Pick up wine bottle from the cabinet.
Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the counter top on your right.
Place wine bottle on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Moving wine bottle from one location to another.
